title: Womb Sounds for Baby Sleep
description:
Spending nine months there, babies naturally grow accustomed to the sound environment of the womb. Turn on this calming sound to help your infant feel safe and relaxed. 

Want access to an ad-free, 8-hour version of this episode? Try Deep Sleep Sounds Premium free for 7 days: https://sleepsounds.supercast.com/.
